# Supabase project credentials for the SPA (Vite env vars, baked at build).
# Copy to .env.local for local dev. Both are also set as GitHub repo
# *variables* for the Pages build. The anon key is public by design
# (sb_publishable_ class) — RLS is the security boundary. The service_role
# key must NEVER appear here. (Full walkthrough lands in Phase 5.)
VITE_SUPABASE_URL=
VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=
